{"tid":365901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實依家需要既係左膠式抗爭","createTime":"2017-08-19T15:15:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-20T02:35:07.000Z","uid":75870,"like":45,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f4e0882675d9ff5bfaf611479af1356e6d946d11","tid":365901,"uid":75870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T15:15:21.000Z","msg":"要改變唔係得一種抗爭手法<br />\n識得靈活運用先係聰明做法<br />\n<br />\n依家係拎光環既好時候<br />\n無光環你淋水都叫暴徒<br />\n有光環你就算掟磚都叫起義<br />\n<br />\n雨革前身都係左膠運動<br />\n人多自然有聲勢 你唔係以為勇武派真係會無啦啦走出黎掟磚啊？<br />\n<br />\n做個聰明抗爭者 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf47025708840d2549a39a754bc7c81074c40175","tid":365901,"uid":91721,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T15:32:53.000Z","msg":"正正係我想講嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且抗爭手法仲可以不止於左膠同勇式咁二元<br />\n仲可以由下而上，例子以二次創作做最低成本嘅抗爭<br />\n<br />\n唔好忘記愛沙尼亞歌唱革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"490e1adf5fc86951f41339779240d26e5cb70bd2","tid":365901,"uid":114801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T15:55:03.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"fdc7624567263732798685bc62e5f668b4e67214","tid":365901,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T15:58:14.000Z","msg":"靈活運用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"149e3813f4662ef1f5a680cab7572592149d31ec","tid":365901,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T15:59:09.000Z","msg":"有道理"},{"pid":"941ac3bf3260995bac7a56c8733c7e2fdcbd54f9","tid":365901,"uid":104443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T15:59:42.000Z","msg":"值得幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇錯抗爭最緊要識得靈活運用唔同方式，左膠式就用嚟凝聚民心，真係要打嘅時候先開拖"},{"pid":"07452f7b7087145319737d8a67120decdb3f0f26","tid":365901,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T16:21:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4111f10ca7e91a3cb364da8d5d776a38dfb6bb70","tid":365901,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T17:00:05.000Z","msg":"又黎「今天我&hellip;&hellip;」？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又黎階段性勝利？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又黎畀d掌聲自己？"},{"pid":"e9589592d579c7c0deff8359046f53b8ad806936","tid":365901,"uid":53687,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T00:46:27.000Z","msg":"你係咪分唔清左膠同和理非嘅分別？<br />\n和理非係一種方式，可以因應情況而變，<br />\n左膠係一種思維，包括快樂抗爭、道德感召、永續社運、慷他人之概，唔認同自己就係鬼呢啲唔要得嘅思想。"},{"pid":"2bfffb8f5c557aa947ddf143e707b104e39c2bc7","tid":365901,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T01:20:15.000Z","msg":"左膠抗爭只係表達不滿，點都稱唔上抗爭<br />\n除非有進一步影響政權行動"},{"pid":"34f422bf038c6984db2c361669acc137ff3fad64","tid":365901,"uid":66736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T01:26:50.000Z","msg":"關光環撚事乜 成王敗寇 贏左咪叫起義 輸左咪暴動囉"},{"pid":"4d204273ed0bfd68e4d16fdb32e3cc63ac9ee331","tid":365901,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T01:30:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n笑死人<br />\n同一招又想再出？<br />\n唱歌都講得出<br />\n屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f3ec6fbae95166cac89e37a4376544e12d4384e","tid":365901,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T02:35:07.000Z","msg":"push"}]}